789
00:44:10.773 --> 00:44:12.733
and they'll kill you in no time.

790
00:44:13.734 --> 00:44:16.612
You wouldn't even get a chance
to plead your case.

791
00:44:17.780 --> 00:44:18.989
He won't let you.

792
00:44:19.073 --> 00:44:21.408
Myeong-gil doesn't care about the truth.

793
00:44:22.076 --> 00:44:24.536
The math tells him to bury you.

794
00:44:26.205 --> 00:44:28.040
I mean.
if there is one person on the planet

795
00:44:28.123 --> 00:44:31.168
who knows every single one
of Myeong-gil's crimes.

796
00:44:31.251 --> 00:44:33.087
that person is you. isn't it?

797
00:44:36.757 --> 00:44:38.967
You know him just as well as I do.

798
00:44:40.344 --> 00:44:45.057
If I plant even the smallest seed
of doubt about you to Myeong-gil...

799
00:44:47.851 --> 00:44:49.353
you are a dead man.

800
00:44:49.978 --> 00:44:50.978
Fuck.

801
00:44:52.022 --> 00:44:53.732
Wait. Damn it.

802
00:44:55.150 --> 00:44:57.319
Why should I die?!

803
00:44:58.112 --> 00:44:59.446
Fuck me!

804
00:44:59.530 --> 00:45:00.406
Im Jang-do!

805
00:45:00.489 --> 00:45:01.949
[screams. groans]

806
00:45:02.032 --> 00:45:03.826
Shut up and listen to me!

807
00:45:03.909 --> 00:45:06.537
If you don't pull yourself together.
you will die.

808
00:45:06.620 --> 00:45:08.622
[shallow breathing]

809
00:45:11.583 --> 00:45:12.793
Tell me everything.

810
00:45:14.586 --> 00:45:17.506
And I will send you to a safe country
far away from here

811
00:45:17.589 --> 00:45:19.550
with more than enough money to live.

812
00:45:20.551 --> 00:45:22.219
I taught Myeong-gil everything.

813
00:45:23.804 --> 00:45:26.432
I know of places
that he hasn't even heard of.

814
00:45:27.057 --> 00:45:28.142
This is a promise.

815
00:45:30.769 --> 00:45:31.937
[shaky breathing]

816
00:45:32.020 --> 00:45:35.107
You were already planning to leave
sooner or later.

817
00:45:36.400 --> 00:45:38.527
I'm giving you the chance to do it.

818
00:45:38.610 --> 00:45:40.446
[shaky breathing]

819
00:45:44.032 --> 00:45:45.033
If I talk.

820
00:45:46.535 --> 00:45:47.828
how much money?

821
00:45:49.830 --> 00:45:50.914
[choking]

822
00:45:50.998 --> 00:45:52.750
I'd answer quickly if I were you..

823
00:45:53.459 --> 00:45:55.085
[Jang-do heavy. rapid breathing]

824
00:45:57.129 --> 00:45:58.213
[coughs]

825
00:45:59.965 --> 00:46:03.135
Myeong-gil and Smile Capital
are going down for good.

826
00:46:03.218 --> 00:46:05.721
- [scoffs]
- After that. you're in Guam.

827
00:46:05.804 --> 00:46:07.389
I know some people there.

828
00:46:08.182 --> 00:46:11.810
You'll have plenty enough
to start a new life.

829
00:46:20.444 --> 00:46:21.528
Get him some clothes.

830
00:46:37.169 --> 00:46:38.489
How long have you worked for him?

831
00:46:39.463 --> 00:46:40.506
Five years.

832
00:46:40.589 --> 00:46:42.341
And what is it you do exactly?

833
00:46:42.925 --> 00:46:46.595
I ensure Mr. Kim's illegal dealings
fly under police radar

834
00:46:46.678 --> 00:46:50.182
and make sure things run smoothly
if the police do sniff around.

835
00:46:50.265 --> 00:46:52.309
All right. but what did you do?

836
00:46:52.392 --> 00:46:54.770
For small stuff.
me and In-beom handled it.

837
00:46:54.853 --> 00:46:57.523
And for bigger things.
we used Kim's service company.

838
00:46:58.148 --> 00:46:59.399
What small stuff?

839
00:46:59.483 --> 00:47:01.485
Like... [groans]

840
00:47:02.027 --> 00:47:03.987
...filming things to use against people.

841
00:47:04.071 --> 00:47:06.406
- [Jang-do panting]
- You threatened Iil Group. am I right?

842
00:47:09.243 --> 00:47:10.244
Tell me.

843
00:47:11.411 --> 00:47:12.913
Look. Mr. Kim made me do it.

844
00:47:12.996 --> 00:47:15.707
He didn't ask you who made you do it.
He asked you what you did.

845
00:47:17.709 --> 00:47:19.711
I gathered some footage
of the Iil Group heir.

846
00:47:19.795 --> 00:47:20.921
And?

847
00:47:21.713 --> 00:47:25.342
[spluttering] We just... We stripped him.

848
00:47:25.425 --> 00:47:26.425
Why?

849
00:47:28.971 --> 00:47:31.056
Tell me everything from the start.

850
00:47:31.139 --> 00:47:32.139
[inhales sharply]

851
00:47:32.724 --> 00:47:35.686
There was a 40-story boutique hotel
being built in Gangnam.

852
00:47:35.769 --> 00:47:38.647
but the company went bankrupt
during the pandemic.

853
00:47:39.690 --> 00:47:40.941
Mr. Kim got wind of intel

854
00:47:41.024 --> 00:47:43.944
that the Iil Group heir
was going to take over the hotel project.

855
00:47:44.027 --> 00:47:45.279
But from whom?

856
00:47:46.113 --> 00:47:49.491
The hotel became an eyesore.
so Seoul City decided to step in.

857
00:47:49.575 --> 00:47:52.160
They were looking for someone with cash.

858
00:47:52.244 --> 00:47:55.914
An assemblyman who plays golf with Mr. Kim
recommended him to the mayor.

859
00:47:57.124 --> 00:48:01.169
He wants the... hotel to become a casino.

860
00:48:03.714 --> 00:48:06.300
Seoul City said they'd grant him
a permit for it.

861
00:48:07.009 --> 00:48:08.343
Mr. Kim got excited.

862
00:48:08.427 --> 00:48:10.554
But the Iil Group heir tried to back out.

863
00:48:11.221 --> 00:48:13.056
so I forced him to cooperate.

864
00:48:13.932 --> 00:48:16.184
How many people have you taken videos of?

865
00:48:16.935 --> 00:48:17.935
Fifty.

866
00:48:19.187 --> 00:48:21.481
And Myeong-gil still has all of them?

867
00:48:21.565 --> 00:48:22.565
Yeah.

868
00:48:23.358 --> 00:48:25.819
He sees people's weakness
as a source of income.

869
00:48:26.737 --> 00:48:30.908
He never gets rid of anything
that's of value to him.

870
00:48:31.575 --> 00:48:33.368
Where does he keep these videos?

871
00:48:33.452 --> 00:48:34.453
[inhales deeply]

872
00:48:35.287 --> 00:48:38.373
He keeps an encrypted hard drive
in a safe inside his bedroom.

873
00:48:38.999 --> 00:48:40.334
But it's this German smart safe.

874
00:48:41.752 --> 00:48:43.462
It has a biometric lock.

875
00:48:44.171 --> 00:48:47.090
And if he knows
there are any issues arising.

876
00:48:47.174 --> 00:48:49.343
he can incinerate everything inside it.

877
00:48:49.426 --> 00:48:51.845
He can press a button on his phone.

878
00:48:51.929 --> 00:48:53.805
and this thing will burn its contents.

879
00:48:53.889 --> 00:48:54.723
Nothing left.

880
00:48:54.806 --> 00:48:57.309
He knows
that this is a double-edged sword.

881
00:48:57.392 --> 00:49:01.229
A weapon in his hands
but evidence for the police.

882
00:49:02.856 --> 00:49:05.442
The service company. is it a gang?

883
00:49:05.984 --> 00:49:06.984
Yeah.

884
00:49:07.361 --> 00:49:08.361
How big?

885
00:49:08.779 --> 00:49:12.157
I believe it's around 30.
but they can get more.

886
00:49:12.240 --> 00:49:13.325
And who runs it?

887
00:49:13.951 --> 00:49:14.993
It's Mr. Jung.

888
00:49:15.494 --> 00:49:17.579
He's basically Mr. Kim's guard dog.

889
00:49:17.663 --> 00:49:19.539
He was an MMA fighter.

890
00:49:19.623 --> 00:49:22.709
but apparently he was banned
for beating a man to death in the octagon.

891
00:49:23.293 --> 00:49:24.670
That's when he was recruited.

892
00:49:24.753 --> 00:49:26.380
Who handles the bodies?

893
00:49:27.130 --> 00:49:28.966
Mr. Jung takes care of that.

894
00:49:29.466 --> 00:49:31.134
Tell me everything you know.

895
00:49:32.594 --> 00:49:33.679
Three years ago.

896
00:49:34.429 --> 00:49:38.183
Mr. Kim had a bit too much to drink
and killed a man with his bare hands.

897
00:49:38.266 --> 00:49:39.476
[sighs]

898
00:49:39.559 --> 00:49:40.894
I was nearby at the time.

899
00:49:40.978 --> 00:49:43.730
so I handled the scene
until Mr. Jung arrived.

900
00:49:43.814 --> 00:49:46.316
He called a 3-ton fish truck
with an aquarium

901
00:49:46.400 --> 00:49:47.818
and carried the body away.

902
00:49:48.777 --> 00:49:52.155
From the way he spoke to the driver.
it seemed like he did this a lot.

903
00:49:52.948 --> 00:49:53.948
The name?

904
00:49:55.826 --> 00:49:57.160
I don't remember the name.

905
00:49:58.954 --> 00:49:59.955
I see.

906
00:50:00.664 --> 00:50:02.374
I know a hospital in Incheon.

907
00:50:02.916 --> 00:50:05.252
I'll call an ambulance.
and you'll get some rest.

908
00:50:05.335 --> 00:50:06.920
Once everything is over.

909
00:50:07.421 --> 00:50:10.841
I'll arrange a flight and ID for you.

910
00:50:15.137 --> 00:50:16.972
Do not try to contact anyone.

911
00:50:18.056 --> 00:50:19.391
Otherwise. he'll find you.

912
00:50:19.975 --> 00:50:20.975
[exhales]

913
00:50:24.771 --> 00:50:26.690
[Du-yeong] Your phone. I'm keeping it.

914
00:50:29.484 --> 00:50:30.484
[Mr. Choi grunts]

915
00:50:34.156 --> 00:50:35.782
Let me ask you one last thing.

916
00:50:38.201 --> 00:50:40.287
Where does he keep his gold stashed?

917
00:50:41.705 --> 00:50:43.248
Only In-beom knows.

918
00:50:44.833 --> 00:50:45.834
Tell me why that is.

919
00:50:45.917 --> 00:50:48.920
In-beom is the only person Mr. Kim trusts.

920
00:50:49.546 --> 00:50:50.630
They met in prison.

921
00:50:50.714 --> 00:50:53.425
and they've saved each other's lives
multiple times.

922
00:50:53.508 --> 00:50:55.802
In-beom would give his life for him.

923
00:50:56.845 --> 00:50:59.014
I don't know everything
Mr. Kim is thinking.

924
00:50:59.514 --> 00:51:01.933
but I know In-beom is like a brother.

925
00:51:03.518 --> 00:51:05.312
[ominous music playing]

926
00:51:19.659 --> 00:51:21.078
[theme music playing]

927
00:53:09.603 --> 00:53:10.603
[theme music ends]
